import React from 'react'; class Character extends React.Component { constructor(props){ super() this.state = { name: props.name } } render(){ return(
{this.props.name}
{props.firstChar.gender}
{props.firstChar.birth_year === "unknown" ? "\u00a0" : props.firstChar.birth_year}
{props.firstChar.hair_color}
{props.firstChar.mass === "unknown" ? "\u00a0" : props.firstChar.mass}
) } } export default Character
